name: 'The Photographer' organic cotton tote bag
description: First printed back in 2008, 'The Photographer' tote bag has been the most popular Cut-Out item to date. To coincide with it being featured in new book, Reinventing Screenprinting, we've reprinted it once more. Screenprinted by hand, on manual equipment using white waterbased ink, the camera design has been printed onto black 100% organic cotton tote bags with long handles. This is the first time it has been printed on organic cotton- yet we've kept it the same price as it has always been. With limited quantities printed, this won't be around for long. Free delivery within the UK, items will generally be received 2-3 days of ordering.
